title: RD - Whitmer, Ibrahim & Masks Return to LA
itunes:title: RD - Whitmer, Ibrahim & Masks Return to LA
description:
Adam and Mark link up and discuss 50th Birthday Parties, a former DEA agent who was present in Washington on January 6th who is now facing criminal charges as a result and the return of mask mandates in Los Angeles. 

Watch this episode on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe to that channel, the exclusive home of Beyond A Reasonable Doubt every Tuesday & Thursday
